04feaa487c3a4d2e3e3602403a350127bd2ae8a7301505b2bdedee6f5bfc1fc38cad14ba619c77bf12dc224cecd9dcf54d2741b3c75bd9d290cf745b63e67c4f  0001-remove-debug-flags-and-werror.patch
"
